      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl tracking-wide text-bone">Part B &mdash; Bonterms Standard End User Agreement</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
          Reproduced unmodified below, as published by Bonterms. Attribution and license notice appear at
